      "span_text": "Conversion to the MDR phenotype of the progenitor strain seemed to have been accompanied, from the outset, with the acquisition of the epidemic phenotype, since at least 13 patients were identified whose isolates showed identical mutations in rpoB, katG, embB, gidB, tlyA, and gyrA. Recently, we showed that the secondary rpoB mutation, V615M, fully restored the fitness defect incurred by the rifampicin resistance mutation S531L  .",
